  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have a Kunai Launcher that fires Kunai and Shuriken at lethal speeds. <br />In place of one of this creatures attacks, it can make a 'Kunai Barrage' attack, using your Taijutsu attack bonus, dealing a number of d6s equal to half your level in piercing or slashing damage. <br />Alternatively, you can set the weapon to burst fire as an Action, releasing a cluster of weapons in a cone. <br />All creatures in a 30-foot cone originating from you must succeed a Dexterity saving throw vs. <br />your Taijutsu Save DC, taking a number of d4s equal to half your level in piercing or slashing damage or half as much on a successful save.</p>",
